content.rendered:
Directed by Aleya Sen

Written by Surabhi Bhatnagar. Aleya Sen. Aleya Sen. Tonoya sen Sharma. Shiv Singh

Cast Taapsee Pannu (Koroli). Saqib Saleem (Sumit). Nidhi Singh (Ayesha). Srishti Shrivastava (Shumi). Ayesha Kaduskar (Geetika). Abhilash Thapliyal (Prashant). Santosh Barmola (Jai) . Rajiv Chabria (Dancer). Mohit Chhabra (Goon). Amrit Kaur Dhillon (Indian Wedding Guest). Ashish Gole (Assistant Manager). Naman Gupta (Wedding Guest). Tina Harris (Lesley (Koroli’s Mum)).Raajkamal Kapoor. Vaunisha Kapoor (Indian Wedding Guest).Jasmine Khan. Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Michael Konieczny (George). Adam Lazarus (Film Crew). Alpesh Malaviya (Indian Wedding Guest). Umair Patel (Musical Artist (archive sound)). Chitrasen Pawar (Villager). B.J. Potter (Karl (as Brian Potter Jr.)). Vickrem Singh (Waiter (as Vickrem Gill)). Arevika Stepanian (Brides Best Friend).Marina Ungureanu. Deepshikha Arora (Party Guest / Lead Dancer (uncredited)). Kishore Bhatt (Boardroom Executive (uncredited)). Silver Levy-So (Wedding Guest (uncredited)). Bob Rawling (Indian Wedding Guest (uncredited)). Stephen Samson (Waiter (uncredited)). Sanjana G. Sandhu (Indain Wedding Guest (uncredited)). Atul Sharma (Indian Wedding Guest (uncredited)). Avinashi Sharma (Indian Wedding Guest (uncredited)). Joanna Shegera (Party Girl (uncredited)). Abuzar Sudhan (Waiter (uncredited)). Stuart Whelan (Boardroom Executive (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Tarun Bali. Jackky Bhagnani. Vashu Bhagnani. Deepshika Deshmukh. Shoaib Ibrahim. Mudit Jain. Kapil Madnani. Ravi Sarin. Yogiraj Shetty

Production Jhakaa. Puja Entertainment (India)
